}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== The FCC internal photos for the [[D-Link DIR-X6060]] show an empty socket where a third BCM43684 radio could be so the design is likely reused for this '''D-Link DIR-X9000'''. Many details are copied from the DIR-X6060 based on this assumption.
